":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 建議唔好用tab 用buffer</blockquote><br />\n係咪因為tab 會keep唔到個NERDTree<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c88e0f34d7bcc4a1e4ee2d215b969f5ed5f62c4","tid":333770,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>splitscreen 都要plugin?<br />\n:sp file<br />\nor<br />\n:vs file<br />\n<br />\n或者如果你用nerdtree，直接hit i or s 就搞掂</blockquote><br />\n唔洗 無話要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係囉，我都冇裝nerdtree, 一樣用到splitscreen:<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">To edit multiple files in split screens:<br />\nvim -o / -O file1 file2    (-o for horizontal split, -O for vertical split)<br />\n<br />\nthen use &quot;CTRL-w&quot; + arrow key to switch between screens</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d9378515eb609f7cc92473ad1e53bdd7c113e3","tid":333770,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"咁我用Notepad ++算吧"},{"pid":"ea286524188695bb466dadf3c1205c3df18e5244","tid":333770,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁我用Notepad ++算吧</blockquote><br />\n要用WINDOWS, 不了"},{"pid":"f2b91518a17d918356c297906410a3379eba09f9","tid":333770,"uid":129876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁我用Notepad ++算吧</blockquote><br />\n要用WINDOWS, 不了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}